Barcelona’s Lionel Messi and Andrés Iniesta, and Real Madrid’s Cristiano Ronaldo are named in shortlist for 2012 FIFA Ballon d'Or prize for best player of the year. (Goal.com)Greek football player Giorgos Katidis is banned from his national team for life after giving a Nazi style salute while celebrating a goal in the 2012–13 Superleague Greece match. (Daily Mail)